list-item.p:
Queuing priorities per call type: incoming calls are answered in accordance with their priorities rather than a first-come-first-served (FCFS) rule. Queuing priorities for eight call types differ from each other as follows:

Highest priority: fund inquiries, English communication;

High priority: banking operations;

Medium priority: CC operations, password;

Low priority: campaign, CC password, credit application follow-up.
